<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Server Error — Own Pay</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #0f172a; color: #e2e8f0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; }
        .container { text-align: center; max-width: 480px; padding: 2rem; }
        .code { font-size: 6rem; font-weight: 800; color: #ef4444; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
        p { color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        a { display: inline-block; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; background: #3b82f6; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-weight: 500; transition: background 0.2s; }
        a:hover { background: #2563eb; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="code">500</div>
        <h1>Something went wrong</h1>
        <p>An unexpected error occurred. Our team has been notified. Please try again shortly.</p>
        <a href="/">Go Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
